ro LLM calls expected). Hard cost cap: $10 USD total; stop if sum > $8. Document in docs/test-results/2026-04-14-level3-scenarios.md. Requires USER participation.","activeForm":"Running Level 3 scenarios","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"21","subject":"Phase 12.1: Final review + tag v1.5.0","description":"Final review (git log main..HEAD). Clean run of all tests + shellcheck. Tag v1.5.0 with annotated message. Push to origin only if user requests.","activeForm":"Releasing v1.5.0","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"10","subject":"Phase 5.2: lib/llm.sh + extended mock + tests","description":"Create scripts/lib/llm.sh (jq-based prompt render for multiline safety; portable timeout via timeout/gtimeout/perl fallback; parses claude -p --json-schema output with error handling for is_error, no_struct, invalid). Create tests/mocks/claude with 6 modes (success/fail/timeout/is_error/no_struct/invalid). Create tests/unit/test-llm.sh.","activeForm":"Building lib/llm.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"1","subject":"Phase 1.1: lib/state.sh + tests","description":"Create scripts/lib/state.sh (session state JSON load/save + mkdir-based portable lock + env fallback for config) and tests/unit/test-state.sh. Must pass all assertions including corrupt state recovery and stale lock cleanup (60s default).","activeForm":"Building lib/state.sh","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"11","subject":"Phase 5.3: lib/validate.sh + tests","description":"Create scripts/lib/validate.sh with manual_title_override (verbatim render) separate from manual_anchor (domain override only). Dedupe clauses, cap via max_clauses, detect identical renders (skip_identical). Create tests/unit/test-validate.sh.","activeForm":"Building lib/validate.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"2","subject":"Phase 1.2: Capture real JSONL fixture from live session","description":"Run a real Claude Code session, capture ~/.claude/projects/*/*.jsonl, scrub sensitive data, save as tests/fixtures/transcript-real-capture.jsonl. Document findings about content type (string vs array) at top of file. Requires USER participation to run interactive session.","activeForm":"Capturing real JSONL fixture","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"12","subject":"Phase 5.4: lib/writer.sh + tests","description":"Create scripts/lib/writer.sh: append custom-title records to transcript JSONL (JSON-safe via jq -nc --arg); return non-zero on failure so callers avoid premature state promotion. writer_get_last_custom_title helper for /rename detection. Create tests/unit/test-writer.sh.","activeForm":"Building lib/writer.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"13","subject":"Phase 6.1: Rewrite rename-hook.sh orchestrator","description":"Complete rewrite of scripts/rename-hook.sh as v1.5 orchestrator: stdin JSON parse, lock+load state, detect /rename native as manual_title_override, parse transcript with cwd, compute delta, decide via scorer (last_processed_signature updated AFTER decision), consume budget/overflow, call LLM, validate, write, promote state only on writer success. Traps split: EXIT captures $? first. Invariant: every early exit 0 MUST set _HOOK_CLEAN_EXIT=1. Update tests/run-tests.sh to walk unit/ and integration/. Do NOT delete v1 yet.","activeForm":"Rewriting rename-hook.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"3","subject":"Phase 1.3: Skill prototype (minimal freeze/unfreeze)","description":"Create minimal scripts/smart-rename-cli.sh with only freeze/unfreeze subcommands, minimal skills/smart-rename/SKILL.md, and docs/test-results/2026-04-14-skill-prototype.md. Validates the skill-invocation mechanism before heavy config/logger investment. Requires manual smoke test in interactive Claude Code.","activeForm":"Prototyping skill mechanism","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"8","subject":"Phase 4.1: lib/scorer.sh + tests","description":"Create scripts/lib/scorer.sh implementing work-score delta + call/skip decision. Signature-based idempotency: last_processed_signature = turn_number:file_size. Same signature skips; same turn with larger file_size proceeds (multi-stop). Handle frozen, force_next, llm_disabled, budget exhaustion, overflow, first/ongoing thresholds. Create tests/unit/test-scorer.sh.","activeForm":"Building lib/scorer.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"18","subject":"Phase 10.1: Level 4 Computer Use scenarios ($10 cap)","description":"Enable Computer Use MCP + macOS permissions. Execute 5 scenarios (smoke, evolution, controls chain, /rename native detection, circuit breaker optional). Hard cost cap: $10 USD. Document in docs/test-results/2026-04-14-computer-use.md with calibration suggestions. Requires USER participation.","activeForm":"Running Computer Use scenarios","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"4","subject":"Phase 2.1: lib/config.sh + tests","description":"Replace config/default-config.json with v1.5 defaults (lock_stale_seconds=60, max_budget_calls=6, etc). Create scripts/lib/config.sh implementing precedence: env > user file > defaults. Create tests/unit/test-config.sh.","activeForm":"Building lib/config.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"14","subject":"Phase 7.1: Expand smart-rename-cli.sh with all subcommands","description":"Rewrite scripts/smart-rename-cli.sh with all 7 subcommands: suggest (empty cmd, consumes budget), anchor (<name>, domain slug + JSONL write first), freeze, unfreeze, force, explain, unanchor (clears both anchor AND override). cmd_suggest must integrate with circuit breaker identically to the hook. Rewrite skills/smart-rename/SKILL.md to document all subcommands. Manual smoke test in interactive session.","activeForm":"Expanding smart-rename-cli","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"15","subject":"Phase 8.1: Integration tests end-to-end","description":"Create tests/fixtures/transcript-v15-qa.jsonl and transcript-v15-pivot.jsonl. Create tests/integration/test-end-to-end.sh covering: Q&A no LLM, feature threshold met, writer failure (state NOT promoted + signature NOT advanced), LLM failure increments failure_count, circuit breaker trips after 3, idempotency same signature, multi-stop signature differs, manual /rename sets override, override persists after new hook, pivot domain changes, force consumes overflow. Run integration + full suite; all must pass.","activeForm":"Writing integration tests","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"5","subject":"Phase 2.2: lib/logger.sh + tests","description":"Create scripts/lib/logger.sh: structured JSONL logging per session, level filter from config_get, JSON-safe construction via jq -nc --arg (never string interpolation). Create tests/unit/test-logger.sh.","activeForm":"Building lib/logger.sh","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"19","subject":"Phase 11.1: Apply threshold tuning from Level 3/4","description":"Review Level 3/4 findings; if thresholds need adjustment, modify config/default-config.json (e.g., first_call_work_threshold) and commit as tune(v1.5).","activeForm":"Tuning thresholds","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"9","subject":"Phase 5.1: prompts/generation.md","description":"Create scripts/prompts/generation.md template with variable placeholders (CURRENT_TITLE, MANUAL_ANCHOR, BRANCH, DOMAIN_GUESS, RECENT_FILES, USER_MSG, ASSISTANT_SUMMARY, RECENT_TURNS) and rules for domain/clauses output matching the JSON schema.","activeForm":"Writing prompt template","status":"pending","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]}],"itemCount":21},"type":"attachment","uuid":"addcaf6d-a408-4b88-b0b5-8f94714ab8e8","timestamp":"2026-04-15T04:00:20.719Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/<user>/Documents/tech_projects/claude-code-smart-session-rename","sessionId":"864ac4a0-b668-4fcb-9887-c3c894467411","version":"2.1.108","gitBranch":"main","slu